    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-02T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-02T11:00:00-05:00" n="376"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d376">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 658.119/681</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Sweden</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Whitehouse</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Stockholm</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-02T17:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 2, 1918, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 9 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3094. Have just received Swedish reply with statistics and explanations regarding
                    the exports to Central Powers. Will telegraph brief <hi rend="italic"
                        >résumé</hi> and send text by direct boat on the 8th.<note n="1"
                        xml:id="d376fn1">No telegraphic <hi rend="italic">résumé</hi> received; text
                        enclosed in despatch No. 1476, Nov. 6, received Dec. 8, not printed. (File
                        No. 658.119/720.)</note> Copy to London.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Whitehouse</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
